 ('251', '145', 'en_us', 'Poggio La Noce\'s video nominated TOP  10 ', '<p>We need your vote!<br> it\'s such a complete surprise, and we\'re so excited that the Poggio La Noce Video was selected for the FINAL of the Wine Spectator Video contest. </p><p> Now we need everyone, and I mean everyone to PLEASE vote for the video \"The Rocky Road to elegant sangiovese\". It\'s easy: go to: <a href=\"http://www.winespectator.com/videovoting\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><u>http://www.winespectator.com/videovoting</u></a><br> click on the video, and click on the \"Vote\" button....<br> Thank you in advance and please share with all your friends!<br> and finally please vote before 9/20/2015.</p><p>and to watch the video, here is its link: <a href=\"http://bcove.me/ssbfiuxt\">http://bcove.me/ssbfiuxt</a></p><p>Thank you for your support.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-09-17 18:23:01', '2015-09-17 19:18:14', 'd5161e7c-a533-4cc6-8962-c153b1ddc729'),
