 ('259', '149', 'en_us', 'Vendemmia time!', '<p>So in the end we managed to get all the grapes in before the rain... yeah!  The teroldego was picked on the 18th and the sangiovese on the 21st and the 22nd, and then the 23rd it rained and rained and rained... This year we were pretty organized with our double sorting tables, one for the grape bunches and the second one for the individual berries, plus we had the nicest group of young students from the European University of Fiesole come and give us a hand. A big thank you to them!</p><p><img src=\"{asset:153:url}\"></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2015-09-27 14:30:33', '2015-09-27 15:42:16', '199b2c10-6c4f-459c-90cf-7fd1e27b9c66'),
