 ('158', '84', '2', '1', 'en_us', '3', '', '{\"typeId\":\"2\",\"authorId\":\"1\",\"title\":\"Decisions, decisions, decisions... April 9, 2015\",\"slug\":\"decisions-decisions-decisions\",\"postDate\":1428590040,\"expiryDate\":null,\"enabled\":1,\"fields\":{\"1\":\"<p>Big Day last Thursday... we were tasting and trying to decide on final blends for next fall\'s releases -- which percentages of which grapes we like best for which bottling -- knowing that the possibilities are infinite! It sounds like fun but it\'s actually a difficult exercise and the worst part is that  one has to spit the wine out ! here in the picture the team: Enzo, Valentino our oenologist and Roberto.<\\/p><p>                                 <img style=\\\"width: 398px; height: 298.5px;\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/www.poggiolanoce.com\\/images\\/pages\\/Blend-tasting.jpg#asset:83:url\\\" unselectable=\\\"on\\\"><\\/p>\",\"25\":\"\",\"2\":\"\"}}', '2015-04-16 10:06:46', '2015-04-16 10:06:46', '7ae9df27-de40-492f-a75c-43f2f346136e'),
