 ('227', 'field', '13', 'en_us', ' paonazzo is our grand reserve wine produced by poggio la noce unlike all the other wines at poggio la noce which are produced with more than 90% of sangiovese grapes paonazzo is a blend of 50% sangiovese and 50% colorino it is produced from the oldest parcel of the poggio la noce single vineyard and only 100 cases are produced it is an explosive stunning blend that boasts a deeply ruby color it is a wine of immense structure and it s meant for serious cellaring coming soon '),
